data.description: Welcome to a captivating historic home from the early 1900s, seamlessly blending vintage charm with modern comforts. Situated on a generous 1.87-acre lot, this property offers a unique blend of history and contemporary living. Inside, discover a cozy gas log fireplace, an oversized utility room, and 3.5 baths featuring elegant fixtures. This house features two primary suites on the main level.  To add to its appeal, the second level includes a full bath and kitchenette and either a third bedroom or a bonus room.. Outside, enjoy the lush 1.87-acre grounds, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. This home is located on a quiet street offering a tranquil retreat from everyday life. Make it yours and create cherished memories.
